    <!-- Slide 25 -->
    <div class="slide-container">
        <div class="slide-header">
            <h1>Technical Evaluation - Automation + Collaboration</h1>
            <div class="slide-number">25</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pid-badge">
            Process Innovation<br>& Digitalization<br>Programme
        </div>
        
        <div class="slide-content">
            <div class="process-flow">
                <div class="process-step step-system">
                    SYSTEM
                </div>
                <span class="arrow">→</span>
                <div class="process-step step-collaboration">
                    COLLABORATION WITH THE PANEL
                </div>
                <span class="arrow">→</span>
                <div class="process-step step-compiling">
                    COMPILING OF INPUT
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="steps-list">
                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-text">
                        <strong>System Screening</strong> - System autofilled technical evaluation
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-text">
                        Procurement Official assigns suppliers/materials/lots or full response tables to evaluators with instructions.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-text">
                        <strong>Collaboration with the panel</strong> - Evaluators each have column for review of 1st draft and possibility to change system prefilled rating, add comments, propose a need for evaluation clarification. Evaluators complete review independently. Can not change each others input.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-text">
                        Procurement official reviews input, requests evaluation clarifications from bidders, reviews any inconsistencies between the ratings.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-text">
                        <strong>Compiling of input</strong> - Based on vendors clarifications (and any further engagement with panel) - procurement official provides final ratings.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    <div class="step-text">
                        <strong style="color: #9b59b6;">FOR RFPs</strong> - instead of pass/fail, system screening is not generated.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <strong>Initial mock-up</strong> - representing the final view/output (collaboration interface). High level draft interface for each evaluator on next slide
            </div>

