            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>Key Features of Individual Evaluator Interface:</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin-top: 10px; margin-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>System auto-populates requirement details from tender authoring</li>
                    <li>Bidder's responses and compliance status are automatically generated</li>
                    <li>Evaluators can override system assessment with justification</li>
                    <li>Comments field enables transparent evaluation rationale</li>
                    <li>Request clarification functionality streamlines vendor communication</li>
                    <li>Individual evaluators cannot see or modify other evaluators' inputs</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
